data.description: Beautiful updated home w/full basement. Large front porch , spacious bedrooms, large bathroom (nice shower in basement).  Large backyard, new roof on home, (May 2015) and newer garage roof, (July 2014). Over $10500 in roofing alone. Fresh paint throughout most of home and new beautiful vinyl in kitchen and bathroom. House comes with reliable newer security system, (2014) already in place. Convenient location, tons of storage space, finished office and gym area in basement. House is literally move-in ready.
